1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,800
(Two months later)

2
00:00:00,880 --> 00:00:06,480
Lang Di.

3
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:43,600
Lang Di's cameo in
the spin-off is trending.

4
00:00:43,638 --> 00:00:44,046
[#3 topic on Weibo]

5
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:46,559
Should we still release the behind-the-scenes
footage that Qi Haoyu's agency rejected?

6
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:47,759
I double-checked.

7
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,919
The contract grants all
promotional rights to our company.

8
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,879
They're only making trouble
now because Sister Lan isn't here.

9
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:52,920
They want to bargain.

10
00:00:55,359 --> 00:00:58,559
Post it. And tell Qi Haoyu to come to
the office for a livestream this Saturday.

11
00:00:58,880 --> 00:00:59,679
Okay.

12
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:01,719
Just have Han Lu WeChat him.

13
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:04,000
The livestream was already agreed upon.

14
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,840
We don't need to go through his agency.

15
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:25,359
Coco, I think I forgot something.

16
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,480
The brewing pot is in my bag.

17
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,599
It's a card I took this morning.

18
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:32,679
It's under the tissue
box in the dressing room.

19
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,079
Sister Jialin, Lang Di is missing.

20
00:01:54,159 --> 00:01:55,120
He told me.

21
00:01:55,121 --> 00:01:56,480
Go back to the office first.

22
00:01:56,800 --> 00:02:04,800
"A Winter Sun Wakes the Wind in Spring Hills' Dream"

23
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:12,300
(Episode 7: Clandestine)

24
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,480
Are there security cameras?

25
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,520
I covered them.

26
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:41,879
How could I say I regret meeting you?

27
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:46,120
And I can't tell you to calm down either.

28
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:49,920
You don't need to be calm around me.

29
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:22,879
Room 927. Just have the robot bring it up.

30
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,800
Who is it?

31
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,720
Food delivery.

32
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:36,519
Are you leaving?

33
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,600
No.

34
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:40,159
Then why are you putting your clothes on?

35
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:41,879
Isn't there a delivery coming?

36
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,680
It's a robot.

37
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,920
You bit my lip.

38
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,519
Mine too.

39
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,079
Didn't I tell you to use the robot?

40
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:11,279
Hello, I am robot Qingtian.

41
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:13,120
Please take your delivery.

42
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:20,879
Someone ordered a
cake to be delivered home.

43
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,920
Who would've thought they couldn't go home,

44
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:25,359
and had to trouble a robot
to bring it to the hotel?

45
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:28,519
Feng Qingtian, your mission is complete.

46
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,319
Tip, please.

47
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:36,800
Happy birthday, Changyang.

48
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:38,079
Hey.

49
00:07:42,632 --> 00:07:44,205
[Qi Haoyu: No time.]

50
00:07:44,258 --> 00:07:46,178
[Calling: Qi Haoyu]

51
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:48,599
Did you not hear me when I said
I don't have time for a livestream?

52
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,079
I'm rehearsing. I don't have time.

53
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:11,839
If I hadn't shown up today,

54
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,799
who would you have eaten this cake with?

55
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,560
As if you wouldn't show up.

56
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:18,920
You're so sure?

57
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,960
I figured you'd reached
your limit of missing me.

58
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,439
I bet you felt the same way.

59
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:33,759
You put your clothes on because
you knew Qingtian was coming.

60
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,840
A kid delivering food...

61
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:36,919
He's very curious.

62
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:39,360
You talk as if you're an adult.

63
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,079
You of all people should know if I am.

64
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,320
Sis.

65
00:08:51,519 --> 00:08:53,679
Qi Haoyu says he doesn't
have time for the livestream.

66
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:55,758
Sister Lan insisted on
casting him back then

67
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:57,278
because he resembles Shi Yuhao,

68
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:58,320
and you resemble Qinglang.

69
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:01,158
But Shi Yuhao is easily influenced.

70
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:03,279
What others say affects him a lot.

71
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:07,160
Qi Haoyu, on the other
hand, has a mind of his own.

72
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,759
Do you like him?

73
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,120
Hard to say.

74
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:16,360
He's alright when he's not being difficult.

75
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:20,200
But I think it's mostly
because of the show.

76
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,559
Sister Lan once said,

77
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,960
anyone who acts in
her shows will fall in love.

78
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,320
Even if it weren't Qi Haoyu,

79
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,360
if someone else played the part,

80
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:31,759
I'd probably feel the same way.

81
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:33,919
I'll contact him.

82
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:38,360
Handle your relationship
carefully. Don't get hurt.

83
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:39,639
Okay.

84
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:42,039
I said I don't have time for a livestream!

85
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,039
Haoyu, can you watch your tone?

86
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,360
Will your company die
if you're not trending?

87
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:48,558
Kevin said repeatedly not to release
the behind-the-scenes footage.

88
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,360
Why did you still post it?

89
00:09:49,361 --> 00:09:50,696
I don't need this kind of publicity.

90
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:53,000
If you didn't want publicity,
why did you take this role?

91
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:55,735
Are you going to say you only want
to do serious dramas from now on?

92
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:58,638
Qi Haoyu, the prerequisite
for you joining this show was

93
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:01,320
that our company holds all
signing and promotional rights.

94
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:03,399
We don't need Kevin's permission.

95
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:06,399
We have the right to release any
behind-the-scenes footage shot on set.

96
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:08,558
Kevin is giving you a hard time now

97
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:11,240
because he wants to use you
to negotiate extra terms with us.

98
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,719
Now that Sister Lan is gone,

99
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,080
he's biting the hand that fed him.

100
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:15,558
If you're going to be like him,

101
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:17,039
I'll kick you out right now.

102
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:19,039
Jialan Shanying won't die without you,

103
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,320
and the entertainment
industry doesn't lack a Qi Haoyu.

104
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,519
Fuck!

105
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,759
When did you learn to smoke?

106
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:06,919
Eleven.

107
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:12,159
I've never seen you smoke before.

108
00:11:13,759 --> 00:11:16,600
You hate heavy smokers.
I didn't want to annoy you.

109
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:21,720
Are you addicted?

110
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,960
No. I don't get addicted to things easily.

111
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,120
What about people?

112
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:41,439
My addiction to people is stronger.

113
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:46,960
What did you come to
the brand gala for last time?

114
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:48,799
To see you.

115
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:54,559
You came to see me
but didn't even say hello?

116
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,840
I was afraid you wouldn't want to see me.

117
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,200
Wenshu said you're
preparing for an assessment.

118
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,720
I'm going to a hunting school.

119
00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:12,120
Are you here to just notify me?

120
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,559
I might not even pass.

121
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,559
If you pass, you'll just leave?

122
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,600
I thought you would understand me.

123
00:13:38,759 --> 00:13:40,120
Rationally, I do.

124
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,320
Emotionally, I can't.

125
00:13:51,519 --> 00:13:52,519
Say you love me.

126
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,759
If I say it, will you stay?

127
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:57,399
No.

128
00:13:59,519 --> 00:14:00,519
Then I won't say it.

129
00:14:04,919 --> 00:14:06,720
Say it. I want to hear it.

130
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,240
No.

131
00:14:10,919 --> 00:14:11,639
Say it.

132
00:14:11,639 --> 00:14:12,519
I won't.

133
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:13,039
Say it.

134
00:14:13,039 --> 00:14:13,840
No.

135
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,240
Say it.

136
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:14,759
No.

137
00:14:14,759 --> 00:14:15,000
Say it.

138
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:15,759
I won't.

139
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:16,320
No.

140
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:16,720
Come on.

141
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:17,720
No way.

142
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:44,159
You should like this
script, "Snow Drum Verse."

143
00:14:45,639 --> 00:14:46,639
Sis.

144
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,640
You didn't scold Coco, did you?

145
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:52,158
No. Since Lang Di spoke up,

146
00:14:52,159 --> 00:14:53,200
I had to comply.

147
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,200
Sis.

148
00:14:55,559 --> 00:14:56,919
You don't have to be like this.

149
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,240
We can actually go back
to how we used to be.

150
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,120
Qinglang.

151
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:06,200
With Sister Lan gone, the
company is facing many challenges.

152
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,599
Many of our ongoing projects

153
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,000
are running into issues.

154
00:15:17,399 --> 00:15:19,199
Your contract expires
at the end of the year.

155
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:22,559
Sis.

156
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:25,119
Actually, I came to the
office to see you today

157
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:26,399
just to tell you...

158
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,759
to prepare the contract. I'm renewing.

159
00:15:35,159 --> 00:15:37,600
We're family, so we don't
need to overcomplicate things.

160
00:15:38,639 --> 00:15:40,398
Sister Lan's kindness to me

161
00:15:40,399 --> 00:15:42,360
won't disappear just because she's gone.

162
00:15:42,919 --> 00:15:44,440
And your kindness to me

163
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:47,240
shouldn't fade just
because Sister Lan isn't here.

164
00:15:49,159 --> 00:15:50,559
There are no conditions between us.

165
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:57,240
I'll take the script home and read it.

166
00:16:10,759 --> 00:16:13,720
Brother Wenshu, look over
there. That's the coffee plantation.

167
00:16:15,919 --> 00:16:17,440
How long does it take to drive there?

168
00:16:17,799 --> 00:16:19,120
About six hours.

169
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:22,159
If Changyang drives, it'll
probably take half that time.

170
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,440
Then I'll call him to come over.

171
00:16:31,519 --> 00:16:32,519
It's so beautiful.

172
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,480
Pull over by the side of the road.

173
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,840
This is the best spot for photos.

174
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,039
I'll take one of you.

175
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,120
Let me take a photo of you.

176
00:17:12,039 --> 00:17:12,839
Let's take one together.

177
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:13,920
Sure.

178
00:17:15,039 --> 00:17:16,039
Chu Shi.

179
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:25,960
Come here.

180
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,358
Help us take a photo.

181
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:28,359
Sure, no problem.

182
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,640
One, two, three.

183
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:38,400
We look like a senior
tour group with a guide.

184
00:17:39,039 --> 00:17:40,518
I've been abroad for too long.

185
00:17:40,519 --> 00:17:41,519
I'm a bit stiff.

186
00:17:41,799 --> 00:17:42,839
Let's take another one.

187
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:46,519
One, two, three. One, two, three.

188
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,359
One, two, three.

189
00:17:50,759 --> 00:17:52,519
One, two, three.

190
00:17:53,759 --> 00:17:55,400
One, two, three.

191
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:57,599
Ah, I'm so tired.

192
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,519
Ah, I'm getting old.

193
00:18:01,519 --> 00:18:03,559
No more photos. Let's go back.

194
00:18:03,759 --> 00:18:04,759
Let's go, Chu Shi.

195
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:19,519
Sister Dong.

196
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:20,575
It must have been a tough drive here.

197
00:18:20,599 --> 00:18:22,599
Well, I couldn't have
gotten here without driving.

198
00:18:23,119 --> 00:18:24,359
This is Mr. Xu.

199
00:18:24,599 --> 00:18:27,759
Hello. The parking lot
is over there. Let's go.

200
00:18:27,937 --> 00:18:29,015
It's not too bad getting here.

201
00:18:29,039 --> 00:18:30,239
But if you go deeper into Molie,

202
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,160
the roads get really rough.

203
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,160
I see.

204
00:18:33,519 --> 00:18:34,519
Over here.

205
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:38,160
Two rooms.

206
00:18:44,519 --> 00:18:45,558
Can we get three?

207
00:18:45,559 --> 00:18:46,759
Yes, we have them. This way.

208
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,200
And then over here...

209
00:18:48,759 --> 00:18:50,399
Tian, I'll grab your suitcase in a bit.

210
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,400
Okay.

211
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:07,359
Mr. Xu, which room is mine?

212
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,760
Let me know if you need anything.

213
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,960
Freshen up, then we'll grab some food.

214
00:19:12,319 --> 00:19:13,160
I'm so tired.

215
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:13,839
I'm going to sleep first.

216
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:14,880
You guys go ahead and eat.

217
00:19:15,319 --> 00:19:16,319
Alright.

218
00:19:34,119 --> 00:19:34,799
Sorry.

219
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:36,119
It's fine. Come on in.

220
00:19:38,359 --> 00:19:39,639
Sister Dong wants us to go eat.

221
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,559
I came to get you.

222
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,440
Okay, I'll be right
there once I get dressed.

223
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,960
I'll wait. It's easy to get
lost here without a guide.

224
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:50,759
Let's go.

225
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,240
Isn't Brother Shi coming?

226
00:19:52,519 --> 00:19:53,959
He's exhausted from driving all day.

227
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:56,880
Out of the three of us, one is
definitely the most exhausted.

228
00:19:57,839 --> 00:19:58,839
None of this is easy.

229
00:20:08,559 --> 00:20:10,479
We can have a barbecue
tonight if we get hungry.

230
00:20:10,759 --> 00:20:12,319
If only Changyang were here.

231
00:20:12,359 --> 00:20:13,798
He's the ultimate all-rounder of Molie.

232
00:20:13,799 --> 00:20:15,200
My brother came last time...

233
00:20:17,839 --> 00:20:19,976
The reason your brother didn't
come this time is also because of him.

234
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,960
I told your brother that
Changyang went home.

235
00:20:23,319 --> 00:20:25,640
Since you like my brother,
why don't you make a move?

236
00:20:29,599 --> 00:20:30,759
Me, not making a move?

237
00:20:31,039 --> 00:20:32,879
I've already invested
tens of millions in him.

238
00:20:33,359 --> 00:20:35,039
Too bad my brother doesn't fall for that.

239
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,159
Over the years, too many
people wanted to invest in him...

240
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:39,119
while harboring ulterior motives.

241
00:20:40,359 --> 00:20:42,575
That's why I can't make it
look like I have ulterior motives.

242
00:20:42,599 --> 00:20:44,119
I have to let things happen naturally.

243
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:49,240
But I feel like my brother is completely
wrapped around Changyang's finger.

244
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,320
Changyang is just too good at this.

245
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:55,599
He perfectly complements
whatever my brother lacks.

246
00:21:02,359 --> 00:21:05,440
What everyone loves is
what they see in others??

247
00:21:05,519 --> 00:21:07,920
The parts of themselves
they lack but desire most.

248
00:21:10,119 --> 00:21:11,119
What about you?

249
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,799
Does Chen Zhu have what you desire?

250
00:21:16,359 --> 00:21:17,359
Yes.

251
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:21,200
But I can't even count them out any longer.

252
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:25,160
I've almost forgotten what his
voice sounds like and how he looks.

253
00:21:31,799 --> 00:21:33,400
Is it a long walk to the dining area?

254
00:21:34,359 --> 00:21:35,359
We're almost there.

255
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:55,920
Why are you so nervous?

256
00:22:02,519 --> 00:22:03,879
My sister just finished her exams.

257
00:22:04,559 --> 00:22:06,359
Old Xu took them both on vacation.

258
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:08,640
Your dad really dotes on your sister.

259
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,800
He's totally whipped. Neither
Wenshu nor I get that kind of love.

260
00:22:13,559 --> 00:22:15,599
Your dad actually dared
to take people on vacation?

261
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:17,280
It's a company team-building trip.

262
00:22:17,359 --> 00:22:19,559
My mom went by taking
my uncle's family slot.

263
00:22:21,039 --> 00:22:22,720
You seem to know a lot about my family.

264
00:22:23,519 --> 00:22:24,759
Wenshu has a big mouth.

265
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:38,240
With ice.

266
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:48,319
If you want to drink Molie coffee,
you can only get it at my place.

267
00:22:54,039 --> 00:22:55,519
Every sip is precious.

268
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:05,799
This Molie tea and coffee...

269
00:23:06,319 --> 00:23:07,839
why do they taste just like you?

270
00:23:08,759 --> 00:23:09,759
What do I taste like?

271
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,200
Let me taste.

272
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:24,240
The wilderness.

273
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:30,759
Is it the [wide open]
wilderness, or is it wild [I am]?

274
00:23:41,039 --> 00:23:42,519
Didn't you say no one was home?

275
00:23:42,839 --> 00:23:43,919
Are we acting like thieves?

276
00:23:44,559 --> 00:23:46,999
Let go. Have you decided
to let me meet your family?

277
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,120
Which room should I hide in?

278
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:51,319
I never thought about
keeping you from my family.

279
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:53,520
Our relationship has
nothing to do with them.

280
00:23:53,559 --> 00:23:55,039
It's only about the two of us.

281
00:23:58,359 --> 00:23:59,799
The memory of hiding you away...

282
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:01,920
shouldn't be part of our story.

283
00:24:05,839 --> 00:24:07,200
We'll face it together.

284
00:24:07,519 --> 00:24:08,759
Leaving our identities behind,

285
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:11,759
I am me, and you are you.

286
00:24:12,119 --> 00:24:14,200
We're just two people
who want to be together.

287
00:24:21,359 --> 00:24:22,359
Uncle Li.

288
00:24:22,759 --> 00:24:23,920
Oh, Changyang, you're here.

289
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:25,495
The boss asked me to grab some things.

290
00:24:25,519 --> 00:24:26,519
Sure.

291
00:24:26,839 --> 00:24:28,160
Oh, you have a friend over?

292
00:24:28,319 --> 00:24:28,960
Yes.

293
00:24:28,961 --> 00:24:30,359
Alright, I'll grab it and go.

294
00:24:40,039 --> 00:24:41,119
Take care, Uncle Li.

295
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,000
You're sweating.

296
00:25:00,599 --> 00:25:01,759
That was an accident.

297
00:25:01,839 --> 00:25:03,359
I told you they wouldn't be back.

298
00:25:04,359 --> 00:25:05,640
I just didn't expect Uncle Li.

299
00:25:26,839 --> 00:25:28,399
Since they're not back, let's run wild.

300
00:25:33,359 --> 00:25:35,519
You being this good to me feels surreal.

301
00:25:36,845 --> 00:25:38,766
I want to test it out myself.

302
00:25:39,599 --> 00:25:40,599
You think I'm too good?

303
00:25:41,359 --> 00:25:42,640
Then teach me how to be bad.

304
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,440
Can't you learn that on your own?

305
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,759
The quality is quite good.

306
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:25,119
Brother Wenshu, can you sleep
after drinking coffee at night?

307
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:27,440
I used to have trouble sleeping.

308
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,495
But now that I drink it so much,
it doesn't affect me anymore.

309
00:27:29,519 --> 00:27:31,200
Good coffee is just like good tea.

310
00:27:31,319 --> 00:27:32,358
If you drink too much, you get drunk.

311
00:27:32,359 --> 00:27:33,735
And once you're drunk,
you fall right asleep.

312
00:27:33,759 --> 00:27:34,879
Then I'll give it a try too.

313
00:27:35,759 --> 00:27:36,759
Here, try this.

314
00:27:36,759 --> 00:27:37,759
Thanks.

315
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,598
Coffee used to make my heart race,

316
00:27:45,599 --> 00:27:46,759
so I rarely drink it.

317
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,400
If the coffee is bad,

318
00:27:48,559 --> 00:27:49,559
uh, that can happen.

319
00:27:49,759 --> 00:27:52,159
I always say that if world
peace ever happens,

320
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,880
everyone will have coffee in
their left hand and tea in their right.

321
00:27:56,519 --> 00:27:58,039
I like that saying.

322
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:00,119
Coffee in the left hand, tea in the right.

323
00:28:01,119 --> 00:28:03,598
True cultural integration should be

324
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:05,160
the assimilation of daily habits.

325
00:28:06,319 --> 00:28:08,399
Even Western afternoon tea

326
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:11,000
originated from tea culture
spreading to the West.

327
00:28:12,519 --> 00:28:13,559
I'm not sleepy anymore.

328
00:28:20,119 --> 00:28:21,159
Let's stay awake together.

329
00:28:26,039 --> 00:28:28,799
I recently came across a tarot
blogger who is incredibly accurate.

330
00:28:30,519 --> 00:28:31,519
Do a reading for me.

331
00:28:31,559 --> 00:28:32,599
What do you want to know?

332
00:28:35,759 --> 00:28:36,759
Hmm...

333
00:28:38,559 --> 00:28:40,086
How about when your brother will accept me?

334
00:28:40,132 --> 00:28:40,712
OK.

335
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:46,759
Does doing this count as
backstabbing Changyang?

336
00:28:48,039 --> 00:28:49,440
His mom backstabbed my mom.

337
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:51,000
It's just karma.

338
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,200
True.

339
00:29:01,039 --> 00:29:02,039
How do I read it?

340
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:05,319
I can't see a timeline.

341
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:12,080
Have you ever done a reading for yourself?

342
00:29:13,519 --> 00:29:15,039
The things I want to know...

343
00:29:15,839 --> 00:29:17,439
have an even more invisible timeline.

344
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,720
The stars shift and the seasons change.

345
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:29,240
Time moves along the orbits of the stars.

346
00:29:30,319 --> 00:29:31,920
I want to see the orbits of the stars.

347
00:29:34,599 --> 00:29:35,920
You can see them when you die.

348
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,400
Why is that?

349
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:39,839
I read a book once.

350
00:29:40,759 --> 00:29:46,119
The author said we can
only see time after we die.

351
00:29:48,559 --> 00:29:49,640
When we're alive,

352
00:29:50,759 --> 00:29:52,200
time is grown into our bodies,

353
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,920
so we can't see it.

354
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:58,319
Growing up, growing old...

355
00:29:58,559 --> 00:30:00,240
isn't that seeing time?

356
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:04,319
Those are just the
shadows time casts on us,

357
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,160
not time itself.

358
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:10,160
When I die,

359
00:30:10,759 --> 00:30:12,599
I'll turn into fireworks
and fly into the sky.

360
00:30:12,759 --> 00:30:14,440
Then, I'll finally meet time.

361
00:30:46,759 --> 00:30:48,136
Lang Di, look at me from this angle.

362
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:49,759
Look at the light, look at the light.

363
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,519
Great, that looks beautiful. Beautiful.

364
00:30:55,599 --> 00:30:57,599
Hold the flowers and look at me.

365
00:30:58,319 --> 00:30:59,559
Perfect, looks amazing.

366
00:31:00,119 --> 00:31:01,319
Okay, let me check.

367
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:02,920
Okay.

368
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:06,640
Lang Di, an iced coffee after this shoot?

369
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:08,000
No ice.

370
00:31:08,519 --> 00:31:09,720
Sure, I'll get on it.

371
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:15,959
Mr. Wan, Lang Di doesn't
like coffee from outside.

372
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,038
I brought some for him.

373
00:31:17,039 --> 00:31:18,519
Just find someone to brew it.

374
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:21,159
The barista at this estate is excellent.

375
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,319
Let Lang Di try it.

376
00:31:22,359 --> 00:31:23,400
He'll definitely love it.

377
00:31:50,319 --> 00:31:52,319
Lang Di, I'm back!

378
00:31:55,759 --> 00:31:56,759
Woohoo!

379
00:32:03,599 --> 00:32:04,720
I went back to the office,

380
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,616
and Sister Jialin said you were
here shooting for a magazine.

381
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:07,758
I was so eager,

382
00:32:07,759 --> 00:32:09,160
I couldn't wait to rush over.

383
00:32:09,559 --> 00:32:10,319
How much was the cab fare?

384
00:32:10,319 --> 00:32:11,319
I'll reimburse you.

385
00:32:12,599 --> 00:32:14,839
Oh, it's far out in the suburbs.

386
00:32:15,319 --> 00:32:17,000
127.87 yuan.

387
00:32:17,319 --> 00:32:18,559
I'll give you 130.

388
00:32:19,319 --> 00:32:21,319
No, not 130.

389
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:23,920
130 sounds like 'parting
ways.' It's bad luck.

390
00:32:24,799 --> 00:32:26,400
Then I'll give you 199.

391
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,960
Let me help you pick out some clothes.

392
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,359
Their taste is just terrible.

393
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:11,759
Lang Di, try this pour-over.

394
00:33:28,799 --> 00:33:30,119
Who brewed this coffee?

395
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:33,519
The estate's barista. Is it not good?

396
00:33:35,039 --> 00:33:37,319
It's terrible. Go call him over.

397
00:33:37,759 --> 00:33:38,759
Oh, okay.

398
00:33:51,319 --> 00:33:54,039
Lang Di, this barista is
actually quite a big deal.

399
00:33:54,359 --> 00:33:56,000
I don't think I can just summon him.

400
00:33:56,759 --> 00:33:57,759
A big deal?

401
00:33:58,319 --> 00:33:59,758
He brews coffee for the top executives.

402
00:33:59,759 --> 00:34:01,319
Oh, that's a bit...

403
00:34:01,599 --> 00:34:02,599
Tell him this:

404
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:03,839
if he doesn't come,

405
00:34:03,840 --> 00:34:04,959
he doesn't need to
show up for work tonight.

406
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,960
Oh, alright.

407
00:34:21,119 --> 00:34:22,399
Oh, if he comes...

408
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,719
Where is he on duty tonight?

409
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:24,920
That's what he asked.

410
00:34:25,119 --> 00:34:26,399
I'm just passing on the message.

411
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,719
Tell him to come over.

412
00:34:27,720 --> 00:34:28,800
I'll tell him in person.

413
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:30,639
Okay.

414
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,359
Yes, you come.

415
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,920
I'll add another shift tomorrow night.

416
00:34:48,039 --> 00:34:50,360
Oh, passing on the message is one thing...

417
00:34:54,519 --> 00:34:55,320
Wande.

418
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:55,920
Huh?

419
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:56,400
Lead the way.

420
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:57,400
Pass on what?

421
00:34:58,039 --> 00:34:59,039
Oh.

422
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:18,599
The big boss's barista
has quite a background.

423
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:20,800
After you, boss.

424
00:35:23,639 --> 00:35:24,920
How did you sneak in?

425
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:28,920
Come here, and I'll tell you.

426
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:33,960
If you don't, I only have half an hour.

427
00:35:34,119 --> 00:35:35,679
I'm afraid you'll think it's too short.

428
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:38,920
I don't mind.

429
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:08,840
Baby, go get ready backstage.

430
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:23,000
Transfer me 199 yuan.

431
00:37:32,039 --> 00:37:34,440
Next time, it'll be 1,999.

432
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:04,519
Xu Changyang officially meets Brother Guo.

433
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:10,599
Tea doesn't show friendship
as deeply as alcohol.

434
00:38:13,119 --> 00:38:14,199
He can't drink.

435
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,480
He gets rowdy when he drinks.

436
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:16,800
Rowdy?

437
00:38:17,199 --> 00:38:19,239
Then I'd love to hear how rowdy he gets.

438
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,880
Even tea can't keep your mouth shut.

439
00:38:22,639 --> 00:38:24,440
Why are you always taking his side?

440
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:27,239
Who's the outsider here?

441
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,000
Changyang.

442
00:38:37,239 --> 00:38:39,440
Let's not dwell on the past.

443
00:38:39,519 --> 00:38:40,679
From now on,

444
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,198
how you treat Lang Di...

445
00:38:42,199 --> 00:38:44,280
I'll be watching you
with eight hundred eyes.

446
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,920
Our Lang Di is the big brother.

447
00:38:47,079 --> 00:38:48,199
Then I'm the second brother.

448
00:38:48,599 --> 00:38:50,840
I have 799 clones.

449
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:53,039
If you dare treat him
badly even a tiny bit,

450
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:55,400
I'll make you lose a piece of yourself.

451
00:38:57,639 --> 00:39:00,639
Brother Guo, we can
still rest for a while longer.

452
00:39:01,199 --> 00:39:02,480
The vacation can be extended.

453
00:39:03,199 --> 00:39:04,280
How long?

454
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,400
Oh, I'm home.

455
00:39:19,679 --> 00:39:21,239
Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

456
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:33,000
Brother Guo won't dare to drive anymore.

457
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:35,199
I'll be your driver.

458
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:41,440
Experienced drivers charge too much.

459
00:39:42,199 --> 00:39:43,320
I'm a novice.

460
00:39:44,440 --> 00:39:47,079
Novice drivers should yield even more.

461
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:51,440
Yield where?

462
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:54,079
So, novice driver,

463
00:39:54,719 --> 00:39:56,679
where are you on duty tomorrow night?

464
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,239
I'll follow the boss's orders.

465
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:05,280
In the wild.

466
00:40:08,119 --> 00:40:09,519
Isn't that tonight's spot?

467
00:40:15,719 --> 00:40:17,198
Qinglang's personal assistant, Brother Guo,

468
00:40:17,199 --> 00:40:19,678
was spotted and photographed
near Brother Guo's house tonight.

469
00:40:19,679 --> 00:40:20,800
Who's in the car?

470
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:21,679
Didn't get a chance to see.

471
00:40:21,680 --> 00:40:22,919
But I heard that.

472
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:25,000
Brother Guo went to the
company first this morning.

473
00:40:25,039 --> 00:40:26,999
Hearing that Qinglang was
shooting a magazine at the manor,

474
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:27,920
he rushed over there

475
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:28,920
and didn't come out.

476
00:40:28,921 --> 00:40:31,399
When he left the manor
tonight, he was in this car.

477
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,400
Play it again.

478
00:40:32,800 --> 00:40:34,880
He waved to two people when he left,

479
00:40:35,519 --> 00:40:37,759
which means there was
someone in the passenger seat too.

480
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:40,800
Zoom in on the license plate.

481
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:42,079
The battery is almost dead.

482
00:40:51,039 --> 00:40:52,238
Can we trace this car?

483
00:40:52,239 --> 00:40:53,239
Yes.

484
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,440
He's back.

485
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:54,800
Good tea.

486
00:41:56,519 --> 00:41:58,480
But the water is terrible.

487
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:02,320
The water in Shangjing
can't compare to Tianyi.

488
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:06,840
You've learned a lot of
skills in Tianyi over the years.

489
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:08,960
The mountain god blessed me.

490
00:42:11,599 --> 00:42:13,440
Besides growing and making tea,

491
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:14,880
what else did you learn?

492
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:18,800
Old boss,

493
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:20,679
this isn't the office,

494
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,039
and I'm not your secretary.

495
00:42:22,679 --> 00:42:23,840
Just speak plainly.

496
00:42:25,079 --> 00:42:26,679
I asked what you learned.

497
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:29,280
Isn't that speaking plainly?

498
00:42:29,639 --> 00:42:31,880
Then I'll be plain too. I learned to love.

499
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:33,280
Changyang.

500
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:35,440
I learned to love only one person.

501
00:42:35,639 --> 00:42:36,639
Stop it.

502
00:42:43,239 --> 00:42:45,119
Bring them back for dinner tomorrow.

503
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,480
Okay.

504
00:42:49,599 --> 00:42:50,599
Yangyang.

505
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:52,239
The day you brought someone home,

506
00:42:52,519 --> 00:42:53,840
Secretary Li saw you.

507
00:42:54,280 --> 00:42:55,519
I don't care if he saw.

508
00:42:56,719 --> 00:42:59,000
Why didn't you tell your
mother you're dating?

509
00:43:00,480 --> 00:43:02,175
Someone who hasn't cared
about me for eight years,

510
00:43:02,199 --> 00:43:03,320
is she really my mother?

511
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:06,198
If I hadn't sent you away back then,

512
00:43:06,199 --> 00:43:08,479
your dad would have ended
up like Li Gang because of you.

513
00:43:09,480 --> 00:43:10,639
Is he really my dad?

514
00:43:10,840 --> 00:43:12,080
It's on the household register.

515
00:43:12,679 --> 00:43:13,679
Changyang.

516
00:43:15,800 --> 00:43:18,160
I thought you would have
grown up by the time you returned.

517
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:20,880
You said you wanted to
go to the hunter school,

518
00:43:21,039 --> 00:43:23,199
and your dad immediately
got someone to apply for you.

519
00:43:24,639 --> 00:43:25,840
That's a separate matter.

520
00:43:26,232 --> 00:43:28,809
I remember the kindness, and
I won't forget the hatred either.

521
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:30,238
Maybe eight years is too short.

522
00:43:30,239 --> 00:43:32,280
Maybe in another 18 or 28 years,

523
00:43:32,400 --> 00:43:33,639
we can let bygones be bygones.

524
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:36,160
If you're going to be like this,

525
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:38,519
don't bring anyone back tomorrow.

526
00:43:41,440 --> 00:43:42,440
Fine.

527
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:48,400
I won't let him put up with your
and Old Xu's attitude anyway.

528
00:43:49,119 --> 00:43:50,719
But out of blood relation,

529
00:43:51,199 --> 00:43:52,719
I should let you know who he is.

530
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:06,639
Changyang, I'm not joking with you.

531
00:44:07,079 --> 00:44:08,320
I'm not joking either.

532
00:44:08,719 --> 00:44:09,999
There's plenty of
information about him online.

533
00:44:10,000 --> 00:44:11,000
You can search for it yourself.

534
00:44:11,001 --> 00:44:12,039
No need for Secretary Li.

535
00:44:14,239 --> 00:44:15,239
Are you home?

536
00:44:15,800 --> 00:44:16,800
Just finished showering.

537
00:44:17,159 --> 00:44:18,000
Let's video call.

538
00:44:18,079 --> 00:44:19,679
No, I don't have clothes on.

539
00:44:33,159 --> 00:44:34,799
Didn't you say you don't have clothes on?

540
00:44:35,199 --> 00:44:36,199
I just put some on.

541
00:44:36,480 --> 00:44:37,480
Are you teasing me?

542
00:44:37,960 --> 00:44:39,038
Do you have work tomorrow?

543
00:44:39,039 --> 00:44:40,535
I'm shooting a video at
the company in the morning.

544
00:44:40,559 --> 00:44:41,816
Meeting a director in the afternoon.

545
00:44:41,840 --> 00:44:43,800
And saving the evening
for the person on duty.

546
00:44:44,440 --> 00:44:45,880
I want to be on duty at your place.

547
00:44:47,159 --> 00:44:49,000
You're getting bolder and bolder.

548
00:44:49,440 --> 00:44:50,440
I've never been timid.

549
00:44:52,199 --> 00:44:53,239
That's too risky.

550
00:44:53,599 --> 00:44:55,198
There are paparazzi all
over my neighborhood.

551
00:44:55,199 --> 00:44:56,199
They stake out every day.

552
00:44:56,400 --> 00:44:57,720
We can go to your parents' place.

553
00:44:59,880 --> 00:45:03,199
- Changyang...
- Are you coming back or not?

554
00:45:25,519 --> 00:45:27,480
I always mess up this last move.

555
00:45:27,960 --> 00:45:29,078
How about we change the move?

556
00:45:29,079 --> 00:45:29,880
Sure.

557
00:45:30,039 --> 00:45:31,119
Let me think.

558
00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:37,920
Okay.

559
00:45:37,920 --> 00:45:38,920
Okay.

560
00:46:04,519 --> 00:46:05,239
This works.

561
00:46:05,239 --> 00:46:06,239
Yeah.

562
00:46:06,320 --> 00:46:07,320
When are you posting it?

563
00:46:07,360 --> 00:46:08,360
Right away.

564
00:46:09,559 --> 00:46:10,880
I'll pick a time.

565
00:46:11,559 --> 00:46:12,880
13:11.

566
00:46:14,880 --> 00:46:15,920
What are you up to now?

567
00:46:18,119 --> 00:46:20,679
Director Li, we are very
keen to work with you.

568
00:46:23,239 --> 00:46:26,559
Sister, does this shoot fit my schedule?

569
00:46:26,719 --> 00:46:28,135
It doesn't conflict with your schedule.

570
00:46:28,159 --> 00:46:29,159
Think about it.

571
00:46:29,360 --> 00:46:29,960
I'll think about it.

572
00:46:29,960 --> 00:46:30,960
Okay.

573
00:46:34,559 --> 00:46:35,559
My phone.

574
00:46:36,280 --> 00:46:37,360
Did you post the video?

575
00:46:37,480 --> 00:46:39,079
Yes, it was scheduled.

576
00:46:40,559 --> 00:46:41,559
How are the comments?

577
00:46:41,840 --> 00:46:43,160
I've been keeping an eye on them.

578
00:46:43,199 --> 00:46:45,960
But there's no comment
from anyone named Ji Zongjun.

579
00:46:46,280 --> 00:46:47,840
Ji Ji Jun, Zong Zong Jun...

580
00:46:47,960 --> 00:46:49,440
Not even Jun Jun Jun.

581
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:55,599
Hey, what does 13:11 actually mean?

582
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:57,000
Decode it yourself.

583
00:46:58,840 --> 00:46:59,960
Morse code.

584
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:01,520
Haha, you really know how to have fun.

585
00:47:03,760 --> 00:47:04,760
Give me a ride.

586
00:47:12,239 --> 00:47:13,000
Brother Guo.

587
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:14,000
Yeah?

588
00:47:21,559 --> 00:47:22,800
You don't like that director?

589
00:47:23,360 --> 00:47:24,638
She's a female director.

590
00:47:24,639 --> 00:47:27,239
She's really nice and just won in
the main competition at Cannes.

591
00:47:28,199 --> 00:47:29,376
Brother Guo, where are you going?

592
00:47:29,400 --> 00:47:30,400
Going home.

593
00:47:34,000 --> 00:47:36,840
Actually, I can just take a cab.

594
00:47:44,159 --> 00:47:45,400
I posted the video.

595
00:47:45,840 --> 00:47:46,879
I can't comment.

596
00:47:46,880 --> 00:47:48,000
It'll cause trouble for you.

597
00:47:48,360 --> 00:47:50,079
You could comment with an alt account.

598
00:47:51,000 --> 00:47:52,159
Why didn't I think of that?

599
00:47:52,199 --> 00:47:53,199
Hold on, let me add one.

600
00:47:53,280 --> 00:47:54,440
Forget it, let's go.

601
00:47:57,800 --> 00:47:59,159
I'll just say it out loud.

602
00:47:59,360 --> 00:48:01,800
A blade's edge comes from sharpening. [Results
follow perserverance + a pun about Molie]

603
00:48:07,565 --> 00:48:12,352
[Commentors saying Qinglang is in
love, wondering who is paramour is, etc]

604
00:48:12,392 --> 00:48:14,458
[The last comment being
what Changyang just said]

605
00:48:16,400 --> 00:48:17,760
Did you change your phone number?

606
00:48:18,400 --> 00:48:19,400
No.

607
00:48:22,280 --> 00:48:23,280
Xiao Yang, Xiao Yang,

608
00:48:23,679 --> 00:48:25,759
help me look up what this string of numbers

609
00:48:25,760 --> 00:48:27,760
means in Morse code.

610
00:48:29,000 --> 00:48:34,960
1311 3331 1131 1

611
00:48:35,360 --> 00:48:39,678
1311 3331 1131 1

612
00:48:39,679 --> 00:48:43,880
In Morse code, this sequence
of numbers translates to "love."

613
00:48:44,360 --> 00:48:45,360
Xiao yang, Xiao yang.

614
00:48:45,559 --> 00:48:49,840
Look up what 1311 stands for.

615
00:50:32,079 --> 00:50:33,559
You know my address...?

616
00:50:35,079 --> 00:50:36,599
You sent a package to Qingtian.

617
00:50:42,360 --> 00:50:44,360
Junjun, have you arrived?

618
00:50:45,280 --> 00:50:46,480
Not yet, Grandma.

619
00:50:46,760 --> 00:50:48,199
We just left the office.

620
00:50:48,559 --> 00:50:50,000
I'm already here.

621
00:50:50,400 --> 00:50:53,760
Even without traffic, it'll take
you an hour and ten minutes.

622
00:50:54,239 --> 00:50:55,760
Don't rush while driving.

623
00:50:56,079 --> 00:50:57,079
I'm in no hurry.

624
00:50:57,280 --> 00:50:59,440
Okay, Grandma. See you soon.

625
00:51:01,599 --> 00:51:03,360
You even have my grandma on WeChat?

626
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:05,360
She loves termite mushrooms.

627
00:51:05,599 --> 00:51:06,799
I send them to her every year.

628
00:51:08,079 --> 00:51:10,800
You prepared for two years to meet [me] in Molie.

629
00:51:11,880 --> 00:51:15,000
Is it possible we met two years ago?

630
00:51:18,679 --> 00:51:19,679
Let's go.
